inghua.edu.cn/anaconda/archive/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-conda&#x4F7F;&#x7528;\"><a href=\"#2-conda&#x4F7F;&#x7528;\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. conda&#x4F7F;&#x7528;\"></a>2. conda&#x4F7F;&#x7528;</h2><h3 id=\"2-1-&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x5305;\"><a href=\"#2-1-&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x5305;\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1 &#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x5305;\"></a>2.1 &#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x5305;</h3><p>&#x5728;&#x6570;&#x636E;&#x5206;&#x6790;&#x4E2D;&#xFF0C;&#x4F60;&#x4F1A;&#x7528;&#x5230;&#x5F88;&#x591A;&#x7B2C;&#x4E09;&#x65B9;&#x7684;&#x5305;&#xFF0C;&#x800C;conda&#xFF08;&#x5305;&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5668;&#xFF09;&#x53EF;&#x4EE5;&#x5F88;&#x597D;&#x7684;&#x5E2E;&#x52A9;&#x4F60;&#x5728;&#x8BA1;&#x7B97;&#x673A;&#x4E0A;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x548C;&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x8FD9;&#x4E9B;&#x5305;&#xFF0C;&#x5305;&#x62EC;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x3001;&#x5378;&#x8F7D;&#x548C;&#x66F4;&#x65B0;&#x5305;&#x3002;</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda list</span><br><span class=\"line\">conda upgrade    --all</span><br><span class=\"line\">conda search nums</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># &#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x5305;&#x64CD;&#x4F5C;&#xFF1A;&#x5B89;&#x88C5; &#x5378;&#x8F7D; &#x66F4;&#x65B0;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">conda install package_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">conda remove package_name</span><br><span class=\"line\">conda update package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>conda &#x8FD8;&#x4F1A;&#x81EA;&#x52A8;&#x4E3A;&#x4F60;&#x5B89;&#x88C5;&#x4F9D;&#x8D56;&#x9879;&#x3002;&#x4F8B;&#x5982;&#xFF0C;s